    <h1>Autonomous Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">AI systems that independently plan, execute, optimize, and report on marketing campaigns with minimal human intervention. The step beyond rule-based automation — decisions made by the system, not scripted by a marketer.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
